descriptor.name: ALMONDS/BADAM 100G
descriptor.short_desc: Almond is the most commonly used dry fruit in india, its often eaten raw or roasted and is used in various dishes like in breakfast, sweets, cookies, pastries, juices, cakes and many more. This dryfruit is rich in protein and regular consumption will reduce risk in heart disease by lowering colesterol levels.
